'''希爾維奧·米卡利''' （{{lang-en|'''Silvio Micali'''}}，{{bd|1954年|10月13日|catIdx=Micali, Silvio}}），出生于[[意大利|意大利]][[帕勒莫|帕勒莫]]，现在在[[麻省理工學院電腦科學和人工智能实验室|麻省理工學院電腦科學和人工智能实验室]]任职的[[计算机科学家|计算机科学家]]。从1983年起，他是[[麻省理工學院|麻省理工學院]]电子工程和[[计算机科学|计算机科学]]部门的一名[[计算机科学|计算机科学]]教授，主要研究[[密码学|密码学]]和[[信息安全|信息安全]]的理论。<ref>{{cite journal|title=A secure protocol for the oblivious transfer (extended abstract)|journal=Journal of Cryptology|doi=10.1007/bf00208002|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/BF00208002|date=1996-06-01|volume=9|issue=3|language=en|pages=191–195|issn=0933-2790|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=M. J. Fischer, S. Micali, C. Rackoff|archive-date=2019-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803093910/https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/BF00208002|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Proofs that yield nothing but their validity or all languages in NP have zero-knowledge proof systems|date=1991-07-01|journal=Journal of the ACM (JACM)|volume=38|issue=3|doi=10.1145/116825.116852|pages=690–728|issn=0004-5411|url=http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=116825.116852|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Oded Goldreich, Silvio Micali, Avi Wigderson|archive-date=2016-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409083317/http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=116825.116852|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0220068|pages=1084–1118|title=Noninteractive Zero-Knowledge|journal=SIAM Journal on Computing|volume=20|issue=6|date=2006-07-13|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1137/0220068|author=Manuel Blum, Alfredo De Santis, Silvio Micali, Giuseppe Persiano|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207165308/https://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0220068|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=IEEE Transactions on Information Theory|title=A fair protocol for signing contracts|date=January 1990|volume=36|issue=1|pages=40–46|doi=10.1109/18.50372|issn=0018-9448|url=http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/50372/|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=M. Ben-Or, O. Goldreich, S. Micali, R. L. Rivest|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207165918/https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/50372/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0218012|pages=186–208|title=The Knowledge Complexity of Interactive Proof Systems|journal=SIAM Journal on Computing|volume=18|issue=1|date=2006-07-13|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1137/0218012|author=Shafi Goldwasser, Silvio Micali, Charles Rackoff|archive-date=2022-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615123828/http://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0218012}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0217017|pages=281–308|title=A Digital Signature Scheme Secure Against Adaptive Chosen-Message Attacks|journal=SIAM Journal on Computing|volume=17|issue=2|date=2006-07-13|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1137/0217017|author=Shafi Goldwasser, Silvio Micali, Ronald L. Rivest|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308025920/https://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0217017|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0217025|pages=412–426|title=The Notion of Security for Probabilistic Cryptosystems|journal=SIAM Journal on Computing|volume=17|issue=2|date=2006-07-13|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1137/0217025|author=Silvio Micali, Charles Rackoff, Bob Sloan|archive-date=2022-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615130335/https://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0217025}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=How to play ANY mental game|date=1987-01-01|publisher=ACM|isbn=0897912217|doi=10.1145/28395.28420|pages=218–229|url=http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=28395.28420|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=O. Goldreich, S. Micali, A. Wigderson}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022000084900709|pages=270–299|title=Probabilistic encryption|journal=Journal of Computer and System Sciences|volume=28|issue=2|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1016/0022-0000(84)90070-9|author=Shafi Goldwasser, Silvio Micali|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314162346/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022000084900709|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0213053|pages=850–864|title=How to Generate Cryptographically Strong Sequences of Pseudorandom Bits|journal=SIAM Journal on Computing|volume=13|issue=4|date=2006-07-13|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1137/0213053|author=Manuel Blum, Silvio Micali|archive-date=2019-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190625233823/https://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/0213053|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="dblp">{{DBLP|id=Micali:Silvio}}</ref>他也是[[区块链|区块链]]平台[[阿尔戈兰德|阿尔戈兰德]]的创始人。

==奖项==
1993年米卡利获得[[哥德尔奖|哥德尔奖]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sigact.acm.org/prizes/godel/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2013-12-21 |archive-date=2010-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100315214752/http://sigact.acm.org/prizes/godel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年，他被选为[[美国工程院|美国工程院]]院士，[[美国艺术与科学院|美国艺术与科学院]]院士。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://theory.csail.mit.edu/awards.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2013-12-21 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206041926/http://theory.csail.mit.edu/awards.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年希爾維奧·米卡利和[[莎菲·戈德瓦塞尔|莎菲·戈德瓦塞尔]]因其密码学的杰出工作获得[[图灵奖|图灵奖]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Goldwasser, Micali Receive ACM Turing Award for Advances in Cryptography|url=http://www.acm.org/press-room/news-releases/2013/turing-award-12|publisher=ACM|accessdate=13 March 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316052703/http://www.acm.org/press-room/news-releases/2013/turing-award-12|archivedate=2013年3月16日}}</ref>。

